the  contractor  in  this  case,  and  from  a  total  lack  of  engineering
education  and  experience  in  general,  and  specifically,  in  the  area
of VTOL aircraft design and controllability of those aircraft.

Chairman MILLER. Mr. Eney, you have visited duPont Aerospace
