airplane,  go  up  to  a  safe  altitude,  where  you  can  recover  the  air-
plane  no  matter  what  goes  wrong  with  it,  and  slow  down  a  little
bit using vectored thrust, then come in and land at that speed, and
take off at that speed for the next flight, slow down a little bit.

VERTICAL TAKE OFF AND LANDING

