idea,  maybe,  to  do  some  direct  research  into  vectored  thrust?  I
mean, that sounds like a good fundamental research concept to me,
to see if it will possibly work.

Again,  I  want  to  commend  the  Chairman  here,  because  we  have
noted  that  it  is  very  easy  to  be  accusatory,  and  I  think  that  this
was  very  well-deserved  here.  People  need  to  be  able  to  ask  you
questions,  and  to  kibitz  with  experts,  to  find  out  whether  or  not
projects  like  this  are  worthy  of  the  research  grants  that  Congress

