CURRENT STATE OF THE DP–2

Chairman MILLER. Mr. Baird.
Mr.  BAIRD.  Thank  you,  Mr.  Chairman,  and  I  thank  the  witness.
Just for the record, I would like to requote former Chairman Hunt-
