thing,  and  asking  questions  that  are  very  reasonable  to  be  asked
of  any  program  that  is  financed  by  the  taxpayers.  And  this  is  the
way we are going to be able to find out the truth, and to make our
own decisions here.

Will  you  all  agree  that  engineers  generally  are  poor  managers?
Any  disagreement  with  that?  I  mean,  am  I  just  sort  of  living  on  a
different  planet,  where  engineers  also  are  great,  you  know,  busi-
