indicate  that  the  contractor  has  brought  forth  considerable  effort
toward  full  implementation  of  standards’’  and  the  type  of  things
that he wasn’t doing the year before. Is that right?

Lieutenant Colonel TREMPER. Yes, sir. That is correct.
Mr.  ROHRABACHER.  Okay.  So,  they  were  lax  at  a  certain  time,
